definition: Wen Zhong (-467 BC), adviser to the state of Yue during Spring and Autumn period

pinyin: ji1 ben3 duo1 wen2 zhong3 ping2 mian4

sentences.english: The King of Yue, Gou Jian submitted and sued for peace.
sentences.chinese: 後越王勾踐臥薪嚐膽，任用文種和范蠡重振國政。

sentences.english: Mulit-lingual processing has become the new focus of Chinese Character Information Processing.
sentences.chinese: 多文種處理已成爲中文信息處理的新熱。
